{"ts": 1777483015.6907756, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:16:55", "type": "agent.started", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483014.693355, "agent": "gamma", "model": "gemini-flash-latest", "provider": "google"}}
{"ts": 1777483017.6440706, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:16:57", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483017.6418314, "agent": "alpha", "line": "The bill includes CPT 99214 and CPT 90837 on the same date of service."}}
{"ts": 1777483017.8873863, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:16:57", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483017.8868766, "agent": "alpha", "line": "Typically, when an E/M service like 99214 is billed alongside psychotherapy (90837), modifier 25 should be used to indicate"}}
{"ts": 1777483018.263344, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:16:58", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483018.261225, "agent": "alpha", "line": "a significant, separately identifiable E/M service."}}
{"ts": 1777483018.2761035, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:16:58", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483018.274239, "agent": "alpha", "line": "The absence of modifier 25 here is concerning."}}
{"ts": 1777483018.4123948, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:16:58", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483018.4108756, "agent": "alpha", "line": "Additionally, CPT 96127 is billed without issues, but the combination of 99214 and 90837 without modifier 25 suggests a"}}
{"ts": 1777483018.4348276, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:16:58", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483018.434313, "agent": "alpha", "line": "potential billing error."}}
{"ts": 1777483018.5714557, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:16:58", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483018.5714557, "agent": "beta", "line": "Looking at this psychiatry claim, I see CPT 99214 (E/M) billed on the same date as 90837 (60-minute psychotherapy) without modifier 25 on the E/M line\u2014"}}
{"ts": 1777483019.0404506, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:16:59", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483019.0385227, "agent": "beta", "line": "that's a clear NCCI edit violation per CMS policy chapter 7."}}
{"ts": 1777483019.9531763, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:16:59", "type": "agent.completed", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483019.9531763, "agent": "alpha", "model": "gpt-4o", "provider": "openai", "verdict": "dispute", "confidence": 0.92, "finding_count": 1, "duration_ms": 5668}}
{"ts": 1777483019.9588685, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:16:59", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483019.95722, "agent": "beta", "line": "The 99214 also references diagnosis pointer C (Z00."}}
{"ts": 1777483020.4230173, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:17:00", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483020.4225037, "agent": "beta", "line": "00, routine exam), which doesn't support medical decision-making for a depression/anxiety visit."}}
{"ts": 1777483021.3669333, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:17:01", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483021.3669333, "agent": "beta", "line": "Additionally, CPT 96127 is billed for 2 units at $28 each, but standardized screening tools like PHQ-9 and GAD-7 are typically"}}
{"ts": 1777483022.3698022, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:17:02", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483022.3687923, "agent": "beta", "line": "bundled into psychotherapy E/M work and shouldn't be separately reimbursed without distinct medical necessity documentation."}}
{"ts": 1777483031.2775493, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:17:11", "type": "agent.completed", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483031.2775493, "agent": "beta", "model": "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929", "provider": "anthropic", "verdict": "dispute", "confidence": 0.89, "finding_count": 3, "duration_ms": 16584}}
{"ts": 1777483050.5996723, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:17:30", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483050.5996723, "agent": "gamma", "line": "The provider billed standalone codes for both an office visit (99214) and psychotherapy (90837) for the same encounter."}}
{"ts": 1777483050.734952, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:17:30", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483050.7344437, "agent": "gamma", "line": "CPT guidelines require psychotherapy to be billed as an add-on code when paired with an E/M service."}}
{"ts": 1777483050.734952, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:17:30", "type": "agent.message", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483050.734952, "agent": "gamma", "line": "Furthermore, the E/M charge lacks the necessary Modifier 25 to indicate a separate, significant service was performed alongside the therapy."}}
{"ts": 1777483052.6304865, "iso": "2026-04-29T10:17:32", "type": "agent.completed", "data": {"job_id": "5dc77973fcf24cd5b7f5e325ad341b1f", "ts": 1777483052.628563, "agent": "gamma", "model": "gemini-flash-latest", "provider": "google", "verdict": "dispute", "confidence": 0.95, "finding_count": 3, "duration_ms": 36946}}
